<li>Bring the dumbbells together so they’re touching, keeping them in line with the center of your chest. This is your starting position.</li>



<li>Engage your core and retract your shoulder blades, pressing your upper back into the bench for stability.</li>



<li>Squeeze the dumbbells together as hard as you can throughout the movement.</li>



